law.catch_line: Short Title -- Kentucky Enterprise Initiative Act.
law.text: KRS 154.20-200 to 154.20-216 shall be known as the Kentucky Enterprise Initiative Act.
law.history: Created 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 168, sec. 44, effective March 18, 2005.

metadata.lrc-note: (3/18/2005). 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 168, sec. 165, provides that this section shall apply to tax years beginning on or after January 1, 2005.
